Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:46.25,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,You can't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:49.50,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Working at an inn is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.60,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,People who aren't interested\Nwon't be able to work long-term.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.26,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there are lots of \Nthings I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.84,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pick the one thing I want to \Ndo the most and make it my career.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:06.46,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Running an inn is not on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 15\NSunny With a Chance of Beans
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Office
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:13.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're very short handed now that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all our waitresses have quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:17.78,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call the union and ask
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if they've got any waitresses available today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:22.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ask around too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:23.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:25.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:26.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:30.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you drifting off for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.50,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd managed them better...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:35.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't the time to be blaming yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:40.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a waitress at Kissuiso,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,so as long as you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:52.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your kindness and concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:53.70,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is our inn's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:03:00.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow a guest of ours \Nto be troubled by our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:03.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're currently on a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:06.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:12.21,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the customers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:17.29,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I want to go here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.29,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:18.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:23.30,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're too nice, Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:25.86,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're on a field trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.82,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:29.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:32.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your free time starts now. \NDon't go too crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Meet back here at 4 p.m. sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:34.94,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.25,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oshimizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.00,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Howdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:44.20,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Time to buy gifts! \NTime to buy gifts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:48.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,For Madam Manager, \Nthe young master,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Jiromaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.38,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoe will love this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.46,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Sake for Mr. Ren,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.14,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,and for Tohru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Tohru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:05.80,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get this for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I can never find one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with my name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:11.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:13.23,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.20,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.41,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:20.82,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.37,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm glad I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:29.27,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, remind me to never work at an inn again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.59,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:33.96,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, working at an inn really {\i1}is{\i0} a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:37.33,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Right, back to gift shopping! Gift shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.82,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:44.00,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's so tiring, and the manual's super specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, the owner's son is such a dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:48.40,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:51.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mango ice cream with \Nfried chicken topping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:52.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:55.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're the pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.86,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:04.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,M-My shoe! And it was brand new too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.91,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Mango ice cream \Nwith fried chicken topping...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.21,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:11.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, blame her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:12.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.16,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.98,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... What did you think you were doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think they were rather callous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.21,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.18,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,They were part-time waitresses at\Nthe inn we're staying at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:37.98,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,They quit without any notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:42.33,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then isn't the inn in a huge mess now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:46.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, they've got to be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:52.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I still think I ought to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:54.97,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about as much trouble as
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 customers suddenly \Nstaying at Kissuiso today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:01.17,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we've only got two groups booked for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's an example!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.17,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,We're allowed to do whatever we want \Nduring our free time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:10.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:11.51,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,H-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Can you buy everyone's gifts for me please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:22.40,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think Jirormaru would
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,love to have something perverted for his gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.24,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.86,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.41,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.42,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,All the inns seem to be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.29,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you sure you \Ndon't need an extra waitress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ohana Matsumae, 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.19,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you supposed to be coming back this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:58.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,After I started imagining a similar \Nsituation happening at Kissuiso,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.31,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of started to panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,How should I explain it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:08.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like a dog who \Nwould love to be fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.00,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No! What am I saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.50,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed that I was drooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:16.22,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that it's a \Nconditioned reflex for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:16.87,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So she's been trained by Mrs. Sui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:25.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She acted on instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:27.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Very few waitresses can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.51,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You know Madam Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was trained at Yunosagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Matsumae.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:40.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:43.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call and let my mentor know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:47.32,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:52.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind helping us out \Nusing your skill as a waitress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:54.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.13,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,The robot collects the dishes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and carries them to the floor above.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.08,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any questions so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:10.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.72,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've been dying to try out your secret weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.69,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.82,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.18,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,If I had done a better job at supervising those part-timers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,none of this would've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:26.60,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. \NYou weren't doing a very good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.65,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.60,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it would be better
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be stricter with part-timers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.49,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,How do things work at your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.53,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,How are the people at Kissuiso supervised?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,With a slap to the face from Madam Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:43.72,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's worse than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It helped me learn my job, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:50.41,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I learned my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:52.34,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Your Madam Manager must be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:56.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I... guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.81,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.96,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:08.82,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.40,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna come and karaoke with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:19.43,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm in the middle of a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:26.28,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Where did everyone disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.71,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me they actually went...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.35,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've got to speed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.10,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.09,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You can't carry that many!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:50.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nakochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:03.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about the gifts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.54,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.81,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,We're also helping out, Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.63,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,We've informed the head clerk already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.33,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought the waitress uniforms!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.05,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.26,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I usually work in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.06,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,How about you and the head clerk take care of the loading,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:24.06,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,while Ohana and I set the tables, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.53,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:26.31,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.94,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming back and helping, Nakochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.14,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that since I couldn't swim right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,working wouldn't be a bad alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.53,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Only this many have been set...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.00,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we make it in time \Nfor the dinner at six.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:52.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We have a secret weapon on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.87,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,But we should hurry, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:55.54,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.46,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.49,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.85,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,The robot's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. It's not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.77,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we'll need to call a mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's the end of our secret weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.28,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:20.29,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.00,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The shower tactic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.29,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.78,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shower...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.29,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,When I was at home, I used it all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:30.71,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,If my mom came home before
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had finished making dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I would send her to have her shower first, and make dinner with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever was left in the fridge while she was in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I called it "The shower tactic!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.72,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,In other words?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.41,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're suggesting that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we ask them all to take a bath first?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.58,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Before dinner is served, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.70,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The shower tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:56.03,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Right, bath time is at six,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.65,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,and dinner's at seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.65,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Adjust everything to that schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.10,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.49,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of the baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.20,Default,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,Waitresses,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please finish setting the \Ntables in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.38,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That was so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:11.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.12,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.93,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wonder what's for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.13,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:19.50,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a change of plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.46,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have your bath before dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:23.51,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, bath time is at six!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:24.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:26.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.77,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.10,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,They're all back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.56,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:36.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.49,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who's excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.90,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they really are working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.51,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... they're festing it up too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:49.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Young master, \Nthe women's bath is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:50.04,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want us to help you over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.31,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I can finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:56.63,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Go help set up the tables instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:58.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:06.29,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:11.31,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Yuina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:15.92,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Sight-see-ing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:23.29,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,This place hasn't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.30,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when we used to \Ntake baths together in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:34.09,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think everything's going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.71,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks to that \Ncurly-haired girl from Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:41.34,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana's hair is a natural perm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.83,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,They're really good-natured,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,helping out in the \Nmiddle of a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.93,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,She's completely different from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.30,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,She's also the granddaughter of an innkeeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner of Kissuiso, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.45,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,She's helping out because she knows
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,precisely how difficult it is to run an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.68,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Question!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:14.00,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you insist on \Ndoing such hard work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:17.50,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think there might be \Nsomething else that would suit you better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:22.46,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Such as being a designer, \Na creator, or even an artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:27.47,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better to do \Nsomething you like as your career!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:31.61,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to get up early in the mornings,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't get any breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.34,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go out and have fun either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:39.62,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,But even then, \Nthere are things I like about this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.74,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,You've never worked, so I doubt you would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:48.74,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I've never worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.85,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.89,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget about our past promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.41,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.50,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like \Nworking at an inn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.54,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no way we can get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:07.47,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who proposed to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now you're calling it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.34,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.43,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I only want to marry someone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who will work here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.81,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like that curly-haired girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.51,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you, Yosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.53,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to work too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.69,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I just choose not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.55,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like Ohana's anything special!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.61,0:15:59.21,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't this slimy stuff coming off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.10,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,It just won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:05.28,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.09,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.73,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,You have to rinse away the \Ncleanser when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.26,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,See, it's all clean now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:31.76,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,How are the preparations coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:35.78,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,We're finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? Yuina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.89,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,5:55 p.m...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.08,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have been able to \Nfinish this without Yuina's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.86,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a blister thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.07,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished setting the tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Just about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone came and helped us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana, we're finished over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.04,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't need us \Nto help with anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:03.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Us waitresses will handle the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:08.00,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the bath's been cleaned, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for you \Ncustomers to enjoy your baths!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that Yuina?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.67,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:16.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, were you cleaning the bath for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:17.78,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:19.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's so clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.89,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I want to go in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.87,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Yosuke Hiwatari, \Nthe head clerk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:31.28,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to say a few words before \Nyou enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:36.55,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You've all gone through a lot \Nof trouble because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:41.83,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to you that we were \Nable to deliver this dinner at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.79,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to represent this \Ninn and thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:49.17,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.76,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You cleaned the bath, Princess Yuina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.80,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.14,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:59.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The princess cleaned the bath for us peasants...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.89,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:03.46,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,I swear never to take a \Nbath in my own home again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:04.73,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.93,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you have some free time later?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.40,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,It was nice of him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to let us have the outdoor bath to ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:26.93,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:28.92,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we managed to finish in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping us, Yuina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.46,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,My blister hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.88,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You got a blister from cleaning the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:38.40,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it was my first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.85,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:46.81,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,This job is really hard work, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.83,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,My blister hurts and so does my hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.81,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I even got really sweaty,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.20,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,but it was surprisingly fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:56.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to sit in an outdoor bath as your thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for your first time working!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it wasn't fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:04.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I was thanked with a slap \Nfrom Madam Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the first time I worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A really hard one at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:09.67,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:11.79,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop exposing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I sleep on a crappy futon, and my roommate is Minchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.16,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,That's got nothing to do with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.92,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get a perverted \Ngift like I asked you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:23.76,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Buy it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.39,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.81,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,If you're drowning, inhale through your nose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and breathe out with your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.15,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.48,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Balut!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:47.26,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Did everyone check their rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.00,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you didn't forget anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:53.91,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,From today, \NI'm going to start studying again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:58.92,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to learn to think \Nabout those who are working.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:01.87,Default,Yusuke,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to learn to think with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of giving them all the work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:05.55,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:09.61,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also going to start learning about inns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:11.39,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You've decided to become Madam Manager?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:12.95,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.00,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,But of Fukuya Inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.46,Default,Yosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.74,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.49,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still undecided.
